========================================================================
 GLXRenderArea Project Overview
========================================================================

 This class derives a class from RenderArea and adds GLX functionality.
 (context creation, triggering redraws etc.)
 
 To use it, create an X-Window drawable and attach it to a
 GLXRenderArea instance.

 See "doc/RenderArea.txt" for more information on using RenderAreas.
 
 See "src/samples/Linux/ConsoleViewer" for an example of how to use
 this class with the native Xlib C api.  

